# Guards

oe14-job-name-guard-commander = Guard commander
oe14-job-desc-guard-commander = The most dangerous person in the neighborhood. Manage a squad of soldiers to ensure the safety of all members of the command.

oe14-job-name-guard = Guard
oe14-job-desc-guard = A fighting unit of the Empire, sworn to protect its people. Watch for safety, and defend others from possible dangers.

oe14-job-name-investigator = Investigator
oe14-job-desc-investigator = Specialist in capturing and neutralizing particularly dangerous magical criminals.

# Trade guild

oe14-job-name-commandant = Commandant
oe14-job-desc-commandant = Control the economy of the settlement by trading with the Empire. Manage stocks and finances by directing resources to the laboring hands.

oe14-job-name-merchant = Merchant
oe14-job-desc-merchant = You have the ability to buy and sell almost anything in your hands! Use this opportunity to surpass your competitors in wealth.

# Mercenary

oe14-job-name-guildmaster = Guildmaster
oe14-job-desc-guildmaster = Establish a connection between the needs of the city and the desires of adventurers to earn money. Organize the delivery of resources and provide adventurers with everything they need for their work.

oe14-job-name-guildworker = Guild Worker
oe14-job-desc-guildworker = Working under the guidance of the guildmaster, issue and accept quests, organize parties of lone adventurers, and train newbies so they don't die from the first fly.

oe14-job-name-adventurer = Adventurer
oe14-job-desc-adventurer = A hunter for thrills, riches and fame, constantly risking his life. Fulfill the most dangerous orders, earning a living by mining resources or killing monsters.

# Artisans

oe14-job-name-alchemist = Alchemist
oe14-job-desc-alchemist = A scientist of sorts, exploring the nature of substances. Create poisons and medicines from numerous natural plants and ingredients and earn money by selling them to people in need.

oe14-job-name-innkeeper = Innkeeper 
oe14-job-desc-innkeeper = Anywhere in Sylate there will be people looking to drink and relax. And you can capitalize on that desire! Find a way to provide people with good rest, food and drink.

oe14-job-name-blacksmith = Blacksmith [Early WIP]
oe14-job-desc-blacksmith = Create and improve equipment for everyone in need! You have the power of metal and fire in your hands, and only you know how to use them carefully to create masterpieces.

oe14-job-name-apprentice = Apprentice
oe14-job-desc-apprentice = A peaceful citizen of the empire, just beginning to learn the subtleties of various sciences. Try to help others in their work, in exchange for a salary and invaluable experience.

# Demigods

oe14-job-name-god-merkas = Merkas
oe14-job-desc-god-merkas = God of purity and healing. TODO

oe14-job-name-god-lumera = Lumera
oe14-job-desc-god-lumera = Patroness of the night sky and knowledge. Expand your influence by helping mortals gain new knowledge.